{"tid":1643275,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天水圍天秀路設「臨時」街市 最快明年底前啟用","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T05:36:22.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6fb2d3ea1fd3269d0932d5193462dc0a3a2e26","tid":1643275,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局宣布，將會在天水圍天秀路公園旁的空地設立<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臨時</span></span>街市，預計最快<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">明年年底</span></span>前完工啟用。<br />\n<br />\n臨時街市將採取「組裝合成」的方式建造，以縮短工程時間，並設有上蓋覆蓋，備有空調。初步計劃設有40個攤檔，集中售賣肉魚蔬果等新鮮食材。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，去年《施政報告》提出在西鐵天水圍站對出的天福路路段興建全新的公眾街市，由於興建新街市需時，局方因此在區內另覓地方設立臨時街市。食衞局、食環署及建築署正與其他相關部門合作推展這個項目，會在適當時候諮詢區議會。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485303-20191010.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485303-20191010.htm&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em%2B6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=486a7adf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485303-20191010.htm&h=03c75be9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485303-20191010.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbd5462fd5eb3e18511316c4b4fcf9dc95eb692","tid":1643275,"uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個位應該係永久街市囉"},{"pid":"5229d35e41ebf21a68fce12d9c51d1a4c00ccae2","tid":1643275,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d3dc537249eebd74c18df453345cdd352d96c5","tid":1643275,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:36:22.000Z","